#Algorand Smart Contract Development Standards

Standards for Algorand smart contract development in this project.

## Project structure
- Don't:
   - reference @algorandfoundation/tealscript
   - use TEALscript
   - add empty @abimethod decorator
   - add @abimethod decorator for Noop
- Do:
   - Use @algorandfoundation/algorand-typescript 
   - use algorand typescript
   - always export the smart contract class
   - always use file extension .algo.ts
   - folder name is snake_case
   - file name is kebab-case

- Good example
```
import { Contract } from "@algorandfoundation/algorand-typescript";

export class HelloWorldContract extends Contract {
  sayHello(name: string): string {
    return `${this.getHello()} ${name}`;
  }

  private getHello() {
    return "Hello";
  }
}
```